    "description": "这是一款由国内个人开发者制作的军事题材单机射击游戏，在游戏中您将扮演机械化车队指挥官，驾驶重装坦克并指挥同伴，在旷野里搜索、刺杀敌军战地指挥首脑。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >点兵</h2>作为指挥官，可以在基地厂房中配置你的<strong>机械化编组</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/4bba90e4bbf8e07fffb3c98e8891e482.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=478 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/4bba90e4bbf8e07fffb3c98e8891e482.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/4bba90e4bbf8e07fffb3c98e8891e482.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >协同冲锋</h2>需要通过键盘和鼠标，驾驶当前选中的装备。<br>作为指挥官可以向其下达命令，标记行进或打击目标<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7a290ca1b855fcd3252fba0de65e0ec7.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7a290ca1b855fcd3252fba0de65e0ec7.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7a290ca1b855fcd3252fba0de65e0ec7.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >隐蔽狙杀</h2>战场上布满敌人的侦察眼线，不要被他们发现，否则会招致更多装甲部队前来支援。<br>远距离刺杀是最好的选择<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/b58f253ec9095ededd43aef87b361622.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/b58f253ec9095ededd43aef87b361622.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/b58f253ec9095ededd43aef87b361622.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >搜索侦查与超视距打击</h2>优秀的指挥官会合理分配车队角色<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>直升机和轮式车辆机动能力强大，深入敌后发现关键目标<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7973626596121fff45536a22ed57226e.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=478 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7973626596121fff45536a22ed57226e.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7973626596121fff45536a22ed57226e.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>标记目标，并实施远程精确打击<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/bc9b07fcdeb0b02edb7b30c97f78dcae.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=478 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/bc9b07fcdeb0b02edb7b30c97f78dcae.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/bc9b07fcdeb0b02edb7b30c97f78dcae.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小心行事</h2>敌人出其不意埋伏在一些关键路段，小心行事！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/1887e0615ab439dbcb00e6454701463d.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=478 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/1887e0615ab439dbcb00e6454701463d.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/1887e0615ab439dbcb00e6454701463d.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >歼灭入侵之敌</h2>突破敌军机械化防线，搜索歼灭入侵者指挥所！！",
